{"id":159825,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/06/联合早报-世界顶级奢侈品折扣中心-中国首家“佛/","date":"2011-06-10T13:30:18Z","modified":"2011-06-10T13:30:18Z","title":"联合早报 | 世界顶级奢侈品折扣中心 中国首家“佛罗伦萨小镇”开业","content":"<div>\n<p>世界顶级奢侈品折扣中心 中国首家“佛罗伦萨小镇”开业</p>\n<p>（2011-06-10）</p>\n<table align=\"left\" width=\"306\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tr>\n<td>\n早报导读</p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.zaobao.com/wapzb.shtml\"><img width=\"300\" height=\"250\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" src=\"http://www.zaobao.com/ssi/bizp/svc/wap300_110421.gif\" /></a></p>\n<table width=\"300\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tr>\n<td valign=\"top\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.zaobao.com/special/china/cnpol/cnpol.shtml\">[中国政情]</a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.zaobao.com/special/china/cnpol/pages4/cnpol110610d.shtml\">什么样的强政府？什么样的强社会？</a><br /><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.zaobao.com.sg/special/us/fincrisis.shtml\">[金融风暴]</a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.zaobao.com.sg/special/us/pages11/fincrisis110610.shtml\">美国面临债务危机比金融海啸严重</a><br /><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.zaobao.com/special/forum/forum_zp.shtml\">[名家专评]</a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.zaobao.com/special/forum/pages8/forum_zp110610a.shtml\">经济实力已取代军事实力？</a><br /><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.zaobao.com/special/china/zaodian/zaodian.shtml\">[中国早点]</a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.zaobao.com/special/china/zaodian/pages2/zaodian_jx110610.shtml\">离京感悟</a></p>\n<table width=\"300\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.zaobao.com/special/services/pages/recruitment_110208a.html\"><strong>联合早报网招聘 Freelance网络新闻编辑</strong></a></td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n<p> 由天津、意大利高端零售品RDM集团共同投资兴建的中国首家“佛罗伦萨小镇”世界顶级奢侈品折扣中心在京津之间的天津市武清区建成，昨天正式开业。</p>\n<p> 佛罗伦萨小镇囊括了近200家意大利顶级奢侈品牌和世界时尚品牌。通向购物小镇中心的石径路上遍布着文艺复兴风格的庭院和长廊。还有设计灵感来自于圣马可广场和一个中世纪的城堡的楼塔，仿建的古罗马斗兽场和1.8公里威尼斯河道。</p>\n<p> 商家希望以平均三至五折的优惠、独特的建筑风格、逛街以及购物环境，给中国消费者带来新的休闲消费体验。</p>\n<p> 图为佛罗伦萨小镇内仿建的威尼斯河道。</p>\n<p> （新华社）</p>\n</div>\n<p><img src=\"http://api.mixpanel.com/track/?data=eyJldmVudCI6ICJmdWxsdGV4dGltcHJlc3Npb24iLCAicHJvcGVydGllcyI6IHsidG9rZW4iOiAiYTRhNDYwYTM5MDRlZWU4ZmY1ZTAyNGVhNGJkZTdhYzIifX0=&#038;ip=1&#038;img=1\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" border=\"0\" /><img src=\"http://pixel.quantserve.com/pixel/p-89EKCgBk8MZdE.gif\" border=\"0\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" /><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://api.mixpanel.com/track/?data=eyJldmVudCI6ICJmdWxsdGV4dGNsaWNrIiwgInByb3BlcnRpZXMiOiB7InRva2VuIjogImE0YTQ2MGEzOTA0ZWVlOGZmNWUwMjRlYTRiZGU3YWMyIn19&#038;ip=1&#038;redirect=http://talkita.com/wrap?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.zaobao.com%2Fzg%2Fzg110610_001.shtml&#038;title=%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E9%A1%B6%E7%BA%A7%E5%A5%A2%E4%BE%88%E5%93%81%E6%8A%98%E6%89%A3%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%83+%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E9%A6%96%E5%AE%B6%E2%80%9C%E4%BD%9B%E7%BD%97%E4%BC%A6%E8%90%A8%E5%B0%8F%E9%95%87%E2%80%9D%E5%BC%80%E4%B8%9A\">Chat about this story w/ Talkita</a></p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/?Sub=750556\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a> <br /><input name=\"EMAIL\" maxlength=\"64\" type=\"text\" size=\"25\" value=\"\"><br />\n<input name=\"FEEDID\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"750556\"><br />\n<input name=\"PUBLISHER\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"7485568\"><br />\n<input type=\"submit\" value=\"订阅!\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":176,"categories":[8779],"tags":[]}